/--
Binary specialization of the constructive `S_b` interval source transformation.

When `|Y| = 2`, the selected nonfocal coordinate is the whole nonfocal
complement, so the single-coordinate `S_b -> S_a` update is automatically a
valid posterior-simplex update.
