`Measure.pi` iid weighted-objective lift for `γ < 1` from a positive base event.
-/
theorem not_measureExpectedDataset_weightedObjective_maximizer_of_iid_allRows_event_dominated
    {X : Type*} [MeasurableSpace X] (μ : Measure X) [SigmaFinite μ] {N K : ℕ}
    (baseEvent : Set X)
